node.text:
having so much fun in california with my boo and to have you guys share in the fun i thought id do a little give back !!
so if you preorder my book today, post your confirmation on your story, and tag me ill pick a person or two to send a little postcard and some goodies to! 
link in my bio!!! cannot believe its only a month away!

node.text:
helllooooo!!! realizing ive never formally introduced myself on here && know theres a lot of new people so thought it would be a good time to do so! 
i’m bella mayo! used to be bella rob, but 2 months ago became the luckiest girl in the world and married my best friend @jacobdmayo ! we currently live in louisiana near our family and with our little black lab puppy who we adore! 
i love to document my life on here and am happy to have so many of you following along :-) over the past few years i wrote a poetry book and my dream of getting it published has finally become reality — my book, titled my greenhouse comes out sept 21st (link in bio!)
my favorite things include my family, my faith, traveling, health & fitness, and helping people anyway i can! i hope through my instagram i can show you love, inspire you, relate to you, or help you in some way! 
comment below if theres anything else ya wanna know about me and ill try and answer! ❤️❤️

node.text: happy golden birthday to the you, @jacobdmayo !! YOU are golden! you make me the happiest girl in the world every single day with your love, strength, and many different voices:-) i couldn’t say enough good things about you! you push yourself, and everyone around you to be the best they can be and anyone who knows you benefits from it! i’m so thankful i get to be your sweet pea, baby girl, and wifey 4ever. I love you the most jacob mayo!!!
